message.en_US: I don't recall hearing anything about new content being added in Rhombus Square...
Especially not deep underground like this place seems to be.
I have no idea who or what could possibly be down here.
I just want to know whose idea it was to have players jump down a deep pit like that in the first place.
Regardless, I'll see if I can find any information on what this place is.
You can feel free to explore this place and see what you can find.
Do you want me to teleport you back up there to see that fun scene again?
